# Pub Quiz Srbija - Environment Variables Template

Kopiraj ovaj fajl u `.env.local` i ispuni sa tvojim vrednostima:

## Supabase Setup

1. Kreiraj nalog na https://supabase.com
2. Kreiraj novi projekat
3. Idi u Project Settings > API
4. Kopiraj URL i Anon Key u .env.local

```
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

## Supabase Database Setup

Kreiraj sledeÄ‡e tabele u Supabase SQL Editor:

```sql
-- Users tabela
CREATE TABLE users (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  email TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  name TEXT NOT NULL,
  avatar_url TEXT,
  auth_provider TEXT NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Questions tabela
CREATE TABLE questions (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  category TEXT NOT NULL,
  difficulty TEXT NOT NULL,
  text TEXT NOT NULL,
  options TEXT[] NOT NULL,
  correct_answer TEXT NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  created_by UUID NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Quiz Games tabela
CREATE TABLE quiz_games (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  score INTEGER NOT NULL,
  total_questions INTEGER NOT NULL,
  accuracy FLOAT NOT NULL,
  answers JSONB,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- Leaderboard tabela
CREATE TABLE leaderboard (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  user_avatar TEXT,
  total_score INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  games_played INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
  accuracy FLOAT DEFAULT 0,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

## Google/Facebook OAuth Setup

1. Idi u Supabase > Authentication > Providers
2. Enable Google i Facebook
3. Postavi redirect URL: `http://localhost:5173/auth/callback`
